logo.png\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-primary/20 blur-3xl -z-10 animate-pulse\"></div></div></div><div class=\"glass-card rounded-full px-8 py-3 inline-block border border-primary/20\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"><span class=\"text-primary font-semibold text-lg\">Faça sua inscrição no Querido Camp</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-center space-x-4 mt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0)\"><div class=\"glass-card w-16 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/30\"></div><div class=\"glass-card w-8 h-8 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-primary/20\"><div class=\"w-3 h-3 bg-primary rounded-full animate-pulse\"></div></div><div class=\"glass-card w-16 h-1 rounded-full bg-primary/30\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 1200 120\" class=\"w-full h-20 fill-current text-primary/10\"><path d=\"M0,60 C300,120 900,0 1200,60 L1200,120 L0,120 Z\"></path></svg></div></div><section class=\"py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-dark to-dark/80 min-h-screen\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-4\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"mb-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><div class=\"p-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-accent/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-alert w-6 h-6\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"8\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12.01\" y1=\"16\" y2=\"16\"></line></svg>Informações de Pagamento</h3><div class=\"space-y-2 text-light\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-lg text-primary\">PIX para Inscrição</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Chave PIX (CNPJ):</span> 63.790.373/0001-23</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Banco:</span> Inter</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Nome Fantasia:</span> Querido Camp</p><p><span class=\"font-semibold\">Titular:</span> Denis Lima</p><p class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary mt-2\">Valor: R$ 75,00</p></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold/20 via-gold/40 to-gold/20 rounded-2xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm -z-10\"></div></div></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"relative group glass-gold glass-hover glass-shine rounded-2xl overflow-hidden \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-white/10 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-50 rounded-2xl pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 h-full\"><form class=\"p-8 space-y-6\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-6\">Dados do Participante</h2><div><label for=\"email\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">E-mail *</label><input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"seu@email.com\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"nomeCompleto\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Nome Completo *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"nomeCompleto\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"Seu nome completo\" name=\"nomeCompleto\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label for=\"idade\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Idade *</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"idade\" required=\"\" min=\"16\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"18\" name=\"idade\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"dataNascimento\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Data de Nascimento *</label><input type=\"date\" id=\"dataNascimento\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" name=\"dataNascimento\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label for=\"estado\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Estado *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"estado\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"Sergipe\" name=\"estado\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"cidade\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Cidade *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"cidade\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"Aracaju\" name=\"cidade\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div><label for=\"nick\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Nick (o mesmo da plataforma Faceit) *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"nick\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"Seu nickname\" name=\"nick\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div><label for=\"faceitLink\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Link do perfil Faceit *</label><input type=\"url\" id=\"faceitLink\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"https://www.faceit.com/...\" name=\"faceitLink\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"gamersClubLink\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Link do perfil Gamers Club *</label><input type=\"url\" id=\"gamersClubLink\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"https://gamersclub.com.br/...\" name=\"gamersClubLink\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"steamLink\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Link da Steam *</label><input type=\"url\" id=\"steamLink\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"https://steamcommunity.com/...\" name=\"steamLink\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><div><label for=\"cpf\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">CPF *</label><input type=\"text\" id=\"cpf\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"000.000.000-00\" name=\"cpf\" value=\"\"/></div><div><label for=\"telefone\" class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Número de telefone *</label><input type=\"tel\" id=\"telefone\" required=\"\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-dark/50 border border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light focus:outline-none focus:border-primary transition-colors\" placeholder=\"(79) 99999-9999\" name=\"telefone\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"bg-dark/30 border border-primary/20 rounded-lg p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-primary mb-3\">Termos sobre Complete</h3><div class=\"text-light space-y-2 mb-4 text-sm\"><p>• O valor para utilizar um complete será de R$50,00 por partida.</p><p>• Isso significa que, se um time X precisar de complete em 3 partidas, o custo total será de R$150,00.</p><p>• O pagamento deverá ser realizado antecipadamente, antes do início da partida.</p></div><label class=\"flex items-start gap-3 cursor-pointer group\"><input type=\"checkbox\" required=\"\" class=\"mt-1 w-5 h-5 rounded border-primary/30 bg-dark/50 text-primary focus:ring-primary focus:ring-offset-0\" name=\"aceitaTermos\"/><span class=\"text-light group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Li e concordo com os termos sobre complete *</span></label></div><div><label class=\"block text-light font-semibold mb-2\">Comprovante de Pagamento *</label><div class=\"relative\"><input type=\"file\" id=\"comprovante\" required=\"\" accept=\"image/*,.pdf\" class=\"hidden\"/><label for=\"comprovante\" class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-3 w-full px-4 py-6 bg-dark/50 border-2 border-dashed border-primary/30 rounded-lg text-light hover:border-primary hover:bg-dark/70 transition-all cursor-pointer group\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-upload w-6 h-6 text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><path d=\"M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4\"></path><polyline points=\"17 8 12 3 7 8\"></polyline><line x1=\"12\" x2=\"12\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"15\"></line></svg><span class=\"font-semibold\">Clique para enviar o comprovante</span></label></div><p class=\"text-light/60 text-sm mt-2\">Formatos aceitos: JPG, PNG, PDF (máx. 5MB)</p></div><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full bg-primary text-dark font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-primary/20 disabled:bg-primary/50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed\" tabindex=\"0\">Enviar Inscrição</button></form></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gra